description: List all folders that a resource is a member of.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID for the Amazon Web Services account that contains the resource.

parameters.name: ResourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) the resource whose folders you need to list.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: Folders
nested_items.description: A list that contains the Amazon Resource Names (ARNs) of all folders that the resource is a member of.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
